body:
**Welcome and thank you for being interested in my research!**


This online-survey is part of my junior research thesis on the E-Sport-phenomenon and deals with its status as a true **&#039;Spectator Sport&#039;**. 

&nbsp;

[**Survey**](http://goo.gl/forms/HHW4RWf4Vl)

&nbsp;

Just note that 
> 'the number of E-Sport-enthusiasts worldwide will grow from 89 million this year to 145 million in 2017' E-Sport is thus far from being a marginal phenomenon and already an integral part of our popular culture. The survey aims to better understand the motivations that drive people and the platforms they use to play and enjoy E-Sports today.

The survey includes 4 pages only, and it shouldn&rsquo;t take you any longer than 10 minutes to complete it. The survey is of course anonymous and cannot be linked to your person.

&nbsp;

[**Survey**](http://goo.gl/forms/HHW4RWf4Vl)

&nbsp;

_Thank you for your support! / Vielen Dank!_

**Kiron J. Hussain**
